name: Jito Staked SOL
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: The first liquid staking derivative on Solana to include MEV rewards. Tracks the price of SOL while accruing staking and MEV rewards. Yield is accrued in the price so it will steadily appreciate vs. SOL.
